com.bigdata.btree.raba.codec

Class RandomKeysGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bigdata.btree.raba.codec.RandomKeysGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IRabaGenerator

    public class RandomKeysGenerator
extends Object
implements IRabaGenerator
    Random B+Tree keys generator. The keys are variable length unsigned byte[]s of up to maxKeyLength bytes. Random byte[]s are generated and then sorted into unsigned byte[] order.
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    Bryan Thompson
